{"tid":1510638,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"帶着膽怯也能繼續前進 - 陳也","createTime":"2019-08-27T09:09:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T09:10:30.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"205e33502c1ee9472da9fa7d11dea7b97eeb1434","tid":1510638,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T09:09:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F/daily/article/20190827/20756361\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E4%25B9%259F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190827%2F20756361&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8biyuJrf%2BHou%2F%2F5XtIYOa%2FW4Y%3D&h=57258013\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E4%25B9%259F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190827%2F20756361&h=93d9f61e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F/daily/article/20190827/20756361</a><br />\n<br />\n帶着膽怯也能繼續前進 - 陳也<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20190827/large/1566806512_d627.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20190827%2Flarge%2F1566806512_d627.jpg&h=f055e647&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n反送中逆權運動走到今天第79日，五年前雨傘運動金鐘清場的紀錄，眼看就要破了。「我們回來了」是真的。有人整理好烏克蘭凜冬烈火運動中至感人肺腑的15句留言，而留言者有的已經壯烈犧牲。香港也有六位殉道者，永遠不要忘記他們巨大的犧牲，牆上紅筆遺言「本人但願可以小命，成功換取二百萬人的心願，請你們堅持下去！」字字入肉，等待一切平靜後就能「收成期」的政府，讀得懂遺言卻仍舊無動於衷，怪不得記者追問林奠「你幾時死」！五大訴求，清楚不過，有司機接載去禮賓府開會的上等人，港鐵淪為黨喉舌封站禁制玩謝居民，上等人齋聽林奠訓話，是永遠嚐不到民間「不合作運動」升級為「黨指揮鐵」的苦鏽。（舔記者鏡頭的核凸大媽、嘴襲陳淑莊的變態大叔想嚐什麼？）<br />\n<br />\n置身79天風眼中，被炒，被砌生豬肉，被射爆（三隻）眼，被山埃照肺，被扣暴動和各式罪名的香港人，讀日本勵志作家旺季志杜香的新書《帶着膽怯也能繼續前進》，與年輕人一起療癒。 <br />\n<br />\n陳也<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n累了嗎？ (尊子)"},{"pid":"dcef21a5bbc82461d84da87703953898e57c4c44","tid":1510638,"uid":52817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T09:10:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NSAWdB2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNSAWdB2.jpg&h=7e1fa5a5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ccb12f5cf262faa580a1a3e25967feb7471e771e","tid":1510638,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T09:10:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PWzcvgg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPWzcvgg.jpg&h=187c67d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8biyuJrf%2BHou%2F%2F5XtIYOa%2FW4Y%3D&h=9196829f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8biyuJrf%2BHou%2F%2F5XtIYOa%2FW4Y%3D&h=f896d733\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8biyuJrf%2BHou%2F%2F5XtIYOa%2FW4Y%3D&h=0f963af6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"}]}